The author of Weave wishes to remain anonymous.

The Weave project was inspired by the blog post "Sniffing World of Warcraft"
at http://bonkel.wordpress.com/2008/03/31/sniffing-world-of-warcraft/

The file "opcodes.h" is based on the file src/game/Opcodes.h from the MaNGOS
Open Source MMORPG server, which is released under the terms of the GNU General
Public License. See http://getmangos.com/ for further information on the MaNGOS
Project.
